name: 泰·布特
introduction: Tai Boothe was born in Los Angeles, California on October 3, 2015. He is an actor and the son of award winning film director, producer and writer Tian Boothe. Tai is of Caribbean, Syrian and white descent and holds American nationality.Tai started acting at the age of one, starring in The Chase (2016) directed by his mother Tian Boothe. He then took on a lead role in the highly acclaimed Shattered Dream (2018). He has then continued on to work on Netflix's Waffles & Mochi (2022) and the upcoming superhero film Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom (2023)Tai attends Grade 1 and enjoys spending his free time painting, building Lego and playing video games with his friends.
